org.sql: SELECT users.id FROM users WHERE users.id IN (SELECT users_settings.user_id FROM users_settings WHERE users_settings.feed_url IS NULL) ORDER BY users.id ASC LIMIT "$1"

rewrites.sql: SELECT users.id FROM users WHERE users.id IN (SELECT users_settings.user_id FROM users_settings WHERE users_settings.feed_url IS NULL LIMIT 1) ORDER BY users.id ASC LIMIT "$1"
